title: Jessy's Party
event: [EVENT_s] wanted go [EVENT_sep] refused kept asking [EVENT_sep] said go [EVENT_sep] went [EVENT_sep] drove [EVENT_e]
text: Jessy wanted to go to a party but none of her friends were going. She refused to go alone so she kept asking all her friends. One of them eventually said they'd go with so she picked her up! They went to the party and all had a great time. After the party Jessy drove home and thanked her friend a lot.
leading_context: Jessy wanted to go to a party but none of her friends were going.
